Package com.example.picmymedcode.Model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BodyLocation
    BodyLocation stores a body location photo and a mark on that photo indicated by the user Note this class is incomplete and will be modified for the next release
    BodyLocationPhoto
    BodyLocationPhoto extends Photo and implements Serializable to add photos
    CareProvider
    CareProvider class extends User class to create a CareProvider object with a patient list.
    Geolocation
    Geolocation class handles the x and y coordinates of a physical location of map
    Patient
    Patient class extends User to create a patient object with a phone number, email and list of problems
    Photo
    Photo class sets the file path of a photo and returns it
    Problem
    Problem class creates a problem object for the patient containing a date, title, description, id, and list of records
    Record
    Record class creates a record object with a title, comment, id, geolocation, photolist, body location, timestamp
    User
    User is an abstract class that provides the common functionality of a Patient and Careprovider (username and userid)
